<h2>PoetrySoup's Website Security Confirmed</h2>

<p>PoetrySoup secures the personally identifiable information you provide on our website in a controlled, secure environment, protected from unauthorized access, use or disclosure. When personal information is transmitted to other Web sites, it is protected through the use of encryption, such as the Secure Socket Layer (SSL) protocol.</p>

