<p>PoetrySoup collects and uses your personal information to operate the PoetrySoup Web site and deliver the services you have requested. PoetrySoup also uses your personally identifiable information to inform you of other products or services available from PoetrySoup and its affiliates. PoetrySoup may also contact you via surveys to conduct research about your opinion of current services or of potential new services that may be offered.</p>

